  ($q$19. Management declaration letter$q$, NULL, '{"Dun & Bradstreet IKEA Due Diligence"}', $q$Statutory Documents$q$, $q$19. Management declaration letter.pdf$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1bUW5vnlL0tPj2ZyyAWP03fHJFA3--l7F/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/pdf$q$, 111383, $q$Management Declaration Letter to Dun & Bradstreet Information Services India Pvt. Ltd. (Mumbai), dated 12-03-2026, part of the IKEA due diligence submission. Declares that neither the signatory nor any of their firms have defaulted on any statutory dues or been involved in any legal case, past or present. Signed by Ramakrishna P Musunuri, Wholetime Director, Macro Media Digital Imaging Pvt. Ltd. (CIN U01119AP1999PTC032909).$q$, now()),
  ($q$15,16,17. List Top 10 Cust & Suppl & Top 5 Contracts$q$, NULL, '{"Dun & Bradstreet IKEA Due Diligence"}', $q$Statutory Documents$q$, $q$15,16,17. List Top 10 Cust & Suppl & Top 5 Contracts.pdf$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Jo_pE2R4DtKvBtx1DsASwpagW-n7a-d6/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/pdf$q$, 170562, $q$Declaration letter to Dun & Bradstreet Information Services India Pvt. Ltd. (Mumbai), dated 12-03-2025, re: Non-Disclosure of Top 10 Customers & Suppliers and reference contacts. States MMDI has NDAs with several customers/suppliers and is therefore unable to disclose their identities or contact details for the due-diligence submission. Signed by Ramakrishna P Musunuri, Wholetime Director.$q$, now()),
