  ($q$18. Latest shareholding pattern FY24-25$q$, NULL, '{"Dun & Bradstreet IKEA Due Diligence"}', $q$Statutory Documents$q$, $q$18. Latest shareholding pattern FY24-25.pdf$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Bpi-LABCwU78u2I5subBj6Cg6V8eUVFU/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/pdf$q$, 185237, $q$Latest Shareholding Pattern / List of Members as on 31 March 2025, Macro Media Digital Imaging Private Limited (CIN U01119AP1999PTC032909). Certified by Dasari Naresh Kumar, Managing Director (DIN 01778737). 10 equity shareholders (Rs.10 face value each): Jasti Srinivasa Karunendra 9,01,500 shares; Musunuri Ramakrishna Prasad 18,01,500; Dasari Naresh Kumar 25,51,500; Nimmagadda Dharma Rao 5,10,300; Pinnamaneni Lenin 12,75,000; Musunuri Sirisha 7,50,000; Jasti Padmaja Rani 3,75,000; Nimmagadda Srikanth 10,20,600; Paruluri Sridevi 10,20,600. Total equity shares: 1,02,06,000.$q$, now()),
