  ($q$12. Insurance Policy Hyderabad$q$, NULL, '{"Dun & Bradstreet IKEA Due Diligence"}', $q$Statutory Documents$q$, $q$12. Insurance Policy Hyderabad.pdf$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/16ea-LNG5jHYFiU8kW9ysZ019T7HHyE_8/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/pdf$q$, 53812, $q$Standard Fire & Special Perils Policy, The New India Assurance Co. Ltd., for Macromedia Digital Imaging Pvt Ltd, Plot No.23B & 24, Phase-5, IDA Cherlapally, Hyderabad-500051. Policy No. 62110111250100000003, period 30/09/2025 to 29/09/2026. Total Sum Insured Rs.60,68,53,000 covering Building Superstructure (Rs.10 Cr), Plant/Machinery/Accessories (Rs.39.08 Cr), Furniture/Fittings/Fixtures (Rs.5.36 Cr), Stocks (Rs.6 Cr), Compound Wall (Rs.25 lakh). Add-on covers: Earthquake (Fire and Shock), Terrorism. Total premium including GST: Rs.11,52,899. Hypothecated to HDFC Bank Ltd, Secunderabad. PAN AABCM9451F, GSTIN 36AABCM9451F1ZF.$q$, now()),
  ($q$MSMED Certificate FY 25-26.$q$, NULL, '{"Dun & Bradstreet IKEA Due Diligence"}', $q$Statutory Documents$q$, $q$MSMED Certificate FY 25-26..pdf$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1NTKbapEmGHDyUQMk7i-QybEmgzu-WYVY/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/pdf$q$, 375032, $q$Udyam (MSME) Registration Certificate. Udyam Registration Number: UDYAM-AP-10-0000987. Enterprise: Macro Media Digital Imaging Private Limited. Enterprise type classification by year: 2025-26 Small, 2024-25 Medium, 2023-24 Medium, 2022-23 Medium. Major activity: Manufacturing. Social category: General. Address: Plot No.44, Apparel Export Park, Autonagar, Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh 530012. Date of incorporation 25/11/1999, commencement of business 23/12/2000. Lists ~17 NIC activity codes spanning fabricated metal products, plastics products, furniture manufacture, machinery repair/installation, architecture/engineering services, interior design/graphic design services, and printing (18115 - printing directly onto textiles, flexographic plastic, glass, metal, wood, ceramics). Date of Udyam registration: 31/08/2020.$q$, now()),
  ($q$4. GST RC Hyderabad$q$, NULL, '{"Dun & Bradstreet IKEA Due Diligence"}', $q$Statutory Documents$q$, $q$4. GST RC Hyderabad.pdf$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QDxRxLaehLe8xKuv4DY59wwkaQ89Bk-J/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/pdf$q$, 296516, $q$GST Registration Certificate (Form GST REG-06) for GSTIN 37AABCM9451F1ZD. Legal/Trade Name: Macro Media Digital Imaging Private Limited. Constitution: Private Limited Company. Principal place of business: 44, Apparel Export Park, Auto Nagar, Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh 530012. Date of liability 01/07/2017, registration type Regular, valid from 01/07/2017 (no end date). Certificate issued 21/09/2017. One additional place of business: Survey No 49, CA4, CFC Area, Autonagar, Mangalagiri, Guntur, Andhra Pradesh 522503.$q$, now()),
