  ($q$MoA & AoA 02 03 2018_MMDI$q$, NULL, '{"Dun & Bradstreet IKEA Due Diligence"}', $q$Statutory Documents$q$, $q$MoA & AoA 02 03 2018_MMDI.pdf$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/146g8KrxoPuUfXP7m63PkW6jdWq0OhBZY/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/pdf$q$, 562568, $q$Certificate of Incorporation, Memorandum of Association (MoA) and Articles of Association (AoA) of Macro Media Digital Imaging Private Limited. Incorporated 25 November 1999 at Hyderabad under the Companies Act 1956, Registration No. 32909 of 1999-2000, signed by Asst. Registrar of Companies K. Padmanabhan. MoA: registered office in Andhra Pradesh; main objects cover media digital printing for advertising, advertising agency services (media space/time buying), and manufacture/purchase/sale/import/export of equipment for the advertising business; extensive list of ancillary objects (R&D, technical consultancy, partnerships/JVs, property acquisition, borrowing, employee welfare funds, etc.). Authorized share capital: Rs.15,00,00,000 divided into 1,50,00,000 equity shares of Rs.10 each. Original subscribers (1999): Jasti Sreekrishna Murthy, Musunuri Ramakrishna Prasad, Dasari Naresh Kumar (100 shares each), witnessed by Pavuluri Achuta Ramaiah (Chartered Accountant); total 300 shares. AoA: private company under Companies Act 2013 Section 2(68), member cap 200, share transfer restrictions, min paid-up capital Rs.1,00,000; covers share capital/calls/lien/transfer provisions, general meetings (21-day notice, quorum 2 members), board composition (2-15 directors, first directors J.S.Krishna Murthy/M.Rama Krishna Prasad/D.Naresh Kumar, non-rotational), Managing Director/additional/alternate/nominee/special director provisions, board powers (borrowing, guarantees, director removal), accounts/audit/inspection/indemnity/secrecy clauses.$q$, now()),
  ($q$2. CIN Certificate$q$, NULL, '{"Dun & Bradstreet IKEA Due Diligence"}', $q$Statutory Documents$q$, $q$2. CIN Certificate.pdf$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/18EfFgaq0FUuvKUPYT8MuzjYlnIwFVVph/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/pdf$q$, 522067, $q$Certificate of Registration of Special Resolution (Section 13(1), Companies Act 2013), issued by Registrar of Companies, Hyderabad, Ministry of Corporate Affairs. Confirms shareholders of Macro Media Digital Imaging Private Limited passed a Special Resolution (AGM/EGM held 28-02-2018) altering the Memorandum of Association's object clause(s). Corporate Identity Number: U01119AP1999PTC032909. Registered 05-04-2018. Signed by Ramesh Chandra Mishra, RoC-Hyderabad. Registered mailing address: Plot No.44, Apparel Export Park, Autonagar, Gajuwaka, Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh 530012.$q$, now()),
  ($q$3. PAN Card$q$, NULL, '{"Dun & Bradstreet IKEA Due Diligence"}', $q$Statutory Documents$q$, $q$3. PAN Card.pdf$q$, $q$https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Pvkk29wpmg7AouC4vV_onyVvYTknr4wh/view?usp=drivesdk$q$, $q$application/pdf$q$, 38304, $q$PAN Card, Income Tax Department, Govt. of India. Holder: Macro Media Digital Imaging Private Limited. PAN: AABCM9451F. Date of incorporation/registration on card: 25/11/1999.$q$, now()),
